Interface DefaultingTransitionFactory<K,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    K -
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    Contexed, TransitionFactory<K,T>

    public interface DefaultingTransitionFactory<K,T>
extends TransitionFactory<K,T>
    TransitionProvider that can generate a default transition for a target if no other transition is specified. This is incompatible with ViewTransitionFactory if both interfaces are implemented the view operation will take precedence.
    Author:
    spb
